 Educational Background



BA International Economics 


Yale University

                  Yale University is an American private Ivy League research university located in New Haven, Connecticut. Founded in 1701 in the Colony of Connecticut, the university is the third-oldest institution of higher education in the United States.                





 Career History



Chief Executive Officer & Co-Founder

                                    Current                


Valimail, Inc.


                  Valimail, Inc. provides email authentication services. It helps the companies to defend email identity and to protect their consumers, brand, and email effectiveness. The firm’s product includes authenticate legitimate email and block phishing attacks as a protection. The company was founded by Alexander Garcia-Tobar and Peter Goldstein and is headquartered in San Francisco, CA.                




Vice President-Corporate & Business Development

                                    2013 - 2015                


Agari Data, Inc.


                  Agari Data, Inc. provides email security solutions. It builds disruptive, Internet-scale, and data-driven security solutions that eliminate email as a channel for cyber attacks and enable businesses and consumers to interact safely. The firm's cloud-based software-as-a-service solution aggregates data from mailboxes to help brands eliminate eMail threats, protect customers and personal data, and guard brand reputation. The company was founded by Patrick R. Peterson in 2009 and is headquartered in San Mateo, CA.                




Chief Executive Officer & Founder

                                    2003 - 2005                


Lattice3D






Director-International Operations

                                    1996 - 1997                


Forrester Research, Inc.


                  Forrester Research, Inc., is an independent technology and market research company, which conducts research and provides pragmatic advice about the impact of technology on business and consumers.  It offers proprietary research, consumer and business data, custom consulting, events and online communities, and peer-to-peer executive programs. The company operates through four divisions: Research, Data, Consulting, and Community. The Research division offers "Whole View" research, which addresses the interplay of business demands and technology capabilities. It provides research services that target industry-specific challenges, trends, business strategists, product developers, and customer experience managers. The Data division offers products and services that focus on consumer and business-user attitudes about technology.  The Consulting division provides research services to assist clients in executing technology and business strategy.  It also assesses viable initiatives for competitive technology gains. The Community division's products are designed to foster connections between peers, analysts, and the relevant research. The company is organized into three client groups: Information Technology, Technology Industry, and Marketing & Strategy. It was founded by George F. Colony on July 7, 1983 and is headquartered in Cambridge, MA.                




Manager-Associate Training

                                    1991 - 1993                


The Boston Consulting Group, Inc.


                  The Boston Consulting Group, Inc. provides management consulting and business strategy advisory services. The firm advises clients in the automotive, pharmaceutical, biopharmaceutical, consumer product, financial, telecommunications, and retail sectors. The company was founded by Bruce Doolin Henderson in 1963 and is headquartered in Boston, MA.                




President & Chief Executive Officer

                                    Prior                


Lattice Technology, Inc.


                  Lattice Technology USA, Inc. provides content and document management software.  Lattice3D's software enables customers to extend their existing 2D & 3D data beyond engineering and into the all aspects of enterprise. It was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in San Francisco, CA.                




Chief Executive Officer

                                    Prior                


SyncTV






