Werlive






Vice President-Business Development & Sales

                                    Prior                


ValiCert, Inc.


                  Part of Sopra Steria Group SA, ValiCert, Inc. is an American company located in Mountain View, CA. The firm develops digital certificate validation software. It was founded by Chini Krishnan. On 23 Jun 03 Tumbleweed Communications Corp. , part of Sopra Steria Group SA since September 2008, acquired ValiCert, Inc. for $24.02 million.                




Professional

                                    Prior                


Sygate Technologies, Inc.


                  Sygate Technologies, Inc. used to Provide security policy enforcement solutions for corporate and personal networks. Its solution offered protecting computers, data and networks from misuse, malicious access and misconfiguration. Its had partnered Alcatel, Aventail, Cisco, Enterasys, Extreme Networks, Hewlett Packard, iPass, Juniper Networks, Microsoft and Nortel to operate across multiple platforms and applications. The company was headquartered in Fremont, CA                





