Terms of Service




















Authentication Services Description
All Authentication Services may be accessed only by Authorized Users and are subject to usage limitations and payment of applicable fees, as more fully set forth in the ValiMail Subscription Terms. 
 
ValiMail's Value Proposition 
ValiMail's service provides Email Authentication as a Service (EaaS). This provides you with the following: 


1)  Visibility into email sent globally claiming to come from your domain(s) _


2)  Improved deliverability thanks to proper authentication _


3)  Protection against email phishing attacks on your employees, clients, and brand _


 
ValiMail's extensive experience with both email and security has created a 'turn-key' solution that is fully automated and shields users from the complexities laid out in earlier sections. Through a unique approach and by partnering with key vendors, ValiMail has abstracted the steps and effort needed to set up DMARC to a simple 'point and click' configuration. Domain owners can configure their domain simply by selecting which third-party services they are using to send email. Power users, who may have their own internal email infrastructure, are supported through additional customization options in our ValiMail Pro service. 
The abstraction ValiMail has performed has several benefits. First, as explained above, it allows for simpler configuration of email authentication, making it accessible even to non-technical users. Second, by automating the process, ValiMail has been able to reduce the cost of implementation by several orders of magnitude. This has enabled ValiMail to offer a solution that is priced appropriately for any organization that wants a low cost, easy to implement DMARC solution. Third, the approach ValiMail has taken has allowed us to fix several existing issues with email authentication, most notably existing restriction on the number of partners who can legitimately send emails on your behalf (e.g., Salesforce, Zendesk, Marketo, Google apps, etc.) for a single domain. 
 
 
 
