ValiMail authenticates legitimate email and blocks phishing attacks. A cloud service based on open standards, ValiMail works with all major ISPs and covers 2.5 billion mailboxes. In full production, our clients span diverse markets ranging from marketplace services to education. Clients include Uber, HBO, and Fenwick & West. 
Problem: Email is a highly effective sales and communication platform, yet increasingly is less trusted and under attack from phishing exploits.
Solution: ValiMail’s mission is to re-build trust in email, and by extension, protect our clients' consumers, brand, and email effectiveness. Our data-driven approach to security allows you to take full control of the email services across your company with the world's first Email Authentication as a Service™.
